Hi:
    The testcase is quite simple:
```verilog
module t (
    input   logic               clk,
    input   logic   [1023:0]    din,
    output  logic   [9:0]    dout
);

logic   [9:0]    shift0;
logic   [9:0]    shift1;

always @ (posedge clk) begin
    shift0 = {100'd0, din[1023-100:0]};
    shift1 = {200'd0, din[1023-200:0]};

    dout = shift0 & shift1;
end
endmodule
```
I'm using the master branch, and I add the -Wno-WIDTH flag.
Here is the generated cpp code:
