I think there are 2 places can be optimized:
1. __Vtemp_he753164e__0 has 1024bit, but only use 10bit, It's better to eliminate the rest variable and assignments
2. Most bits of __Vtemp_h40cba9a7__0 and __Vtemp_hb4749a7f__0 are completely same. It's better to maintain 1 Vtemp and only assign once, rather than multiple Vtemps with multiple assignments
